		{"id":"patronscraper01","type":"text","x":1380,"y":580,"width":540,"height":150,"text":"## Patrón común\n\n```\nfetch.rb → parse.rb → CSV estructurado\n```\n\nRuby 2.6+ | `mechanize` + `nokogiri` | CLI: `optimist`\n\nSin BD, sin tests, sin CI, sin Docker\nMisma estructura de salida en todos los scrapers","color":"2"},
